### 5.2 Maestro AI Evaluation

Create `/src/lib/session/maestro-evaluation.ts`:

```typescript
interface MaestroEvaluationParams {
  messages: Message[];
  maestroId: string;
  studentProfile: ExtendedStudentProfile;
  sessionDuration: number;
}

interface MaestroEvaluation {
  score: number;        // 1-10
  feedback: string;     // Italian feedback
  strengths: string[];  // What went well
